race.comment: OUR BOY CHOPPER (1) boasts a strong record this course with eight wins and two minors from 15 tries. Missed the frame latest (19.74) when sixth over 366m at this track in a OPEN. Expected to go close. CASINO SPECIAL (2) is coming off a 2.5 lengths sixth but in a swift 19.89 at this track over 366m. Expected to feature. MEPUNGA ROCKY (7) had been super consistent recording two placings in a row before he was rewarded with a win last time, scoring at this track over 366m (19.70). Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. MORE THAN MONEY (5) will be hard to beat with a drop in trip.
